title: Fresh Money Flows to Crypto as Stablecoin Market Expands After 1.5 Years Downtrend
description: Tether's USDT added $7 billion to its market cap since September, a sign of capital entering the crypto market, Matrixport noted.

title: SEC Delays Grayscale Ethereum ETF, Confirms Receipt of BlackRock ETH Fund
description: Grayscale will have to wait until late January 2024 to learn the fate of its request to covert its Ethereum trust into an ETF.
